{"tid":2475001,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過撈埋歌詞黎唱","createTime":"2021-04-04T11:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:46:51.000Z","uid":302248,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4328f8ed5de30e70c0664902ca46d42819197b","tid":2475001,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"覺得隔離同無賴幾襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n誰知我上傳十個限時動態定時直播<br />\n醉過喊過期待有他深切慰問我<br />\n但是你死都不變心 跟 我笑著捱<br />\n就算壞我也不忍心 偷偷作怪"},{"pid":"c256ee2d9ac8524c4d30c44b836835e64ef298d9","tid":2475001,"uid":92442,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"誰知我上傳十個限時動態定時直播<br />\n醉過喊過期待有他深切慰問我<br />\n朝朝暮暮讓你猜想如何馴服我 <br />\n若果親手抱住 或者不必如此<br />\n<br />\n誰管我  獨來獨往大時大節未提及我<br />\n每晚勉強全面離線未見得更易過<br />\n春天分手 秋天會習慣<br />\n苦沖開了便淡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47b6e86202b9a3a58b656b4a3deb3f1851fee3c","tid":2475001,"uid":92442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"原來是世間太荒謬<br />\n你我分的手先最合理與溫柔<br />\n裱起婚紗照那道牆<br />\n及一切美麗舊年華<br />\n明日同步拆下<br />\n<br />\n跟你試過遷就<br />\n痛也不分手 先至悟到人世裡<br />\n溫馨的光境不過借出 到期拿回嗎？<br />\n等不到下一代 是嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecbb0d140c9dd49a728513dd374727b008ddf1d","tid":2475001,"uid":46896,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T11:30:32.000Z","msg":"暴君 心裡感謝神"},{"pid":"285fd2d2fafb6b7c855f154fc78e82cb6c39fbdf","tid":2475001,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017171883e26e9e38652204e90dcb50659556800","tid":2475001,"uid":185651,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"愛你 不是因為你的美而已<br />\n我越來越愛你 每個眼神觸動我的心<br />\n<br />\n最愛你的是我 否則你怎麼讓我<br />\n否則我怎麼可能 赴湯蹈火 你說甚麼都做<br />\n<br />\n如果這就是愛 在轉身就該勇敢留下來<br />\n就算受傷 就算流淚 都是生命裡溫柔灌溉<br />\n<br />\n我要變成 童話裡 你愛的那個天使<br />\n張開雙手變成翅膀守護你<br />\n你要相信 相信我們會像童話故事裡"},{"pid":"6db3f5a6cee83f1e9287a78934c0b4354b0db218","tid":2475001,"uid":14208,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"潛龍勿用，極待撫慰"},{"pid":"e5fa4b8bd15e1e922246a173df016fcc9d35fb18","tid":2475001,"uid":176915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"榮華臘腸 家家讚賞<br />\nbillie jeans is not my love"},{"pid":"b2f2ac6b57c938fe2459714522e60128b5ce0faf","tid":2475001,"uid":35107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"滄海一聲笑 聲聲送舊年"},{"pid":"2ed52583c242d23f307e8db64fb147139698749f","tid":2475001,"uid":168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"It's my life<br />\n笑喊憤怒像無形"},{"pid":"b63568a8995e21928ba1e7a359aaf45ba413ac74","tid":2475001,"uid":241850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"遇怪魔我即刻變大個<br />\n迎接光輝歲月<br />\n風雨中抱緊自由"},{"pid":"84368b30cbcb1d6ace7754d7c309b06c4e3aaaa6","tid":2475001,"uid":166062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"遇怪魔我即刻變大個 迎接光輝歲月"},{"pid":"c42b09e92310377a365314cf6825de3c696fec6f","tid":2475001,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"兩眼一刻然後失控<br />\n無謂再   喜歡你<br />\n那可愛臉容"},{"pid":"812aa4a6274ca4bf69d84f2958bf4d1161bfb98c","tid":2475001,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b63568a8995e2192